<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>About - HelloStore</title>

  <style>
    /* ===== BASE PAGE STYLE (MATCH INDEX) ===== */
    body.about-body {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
      color: #fff;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #4e73df, #1cc88a);
      overflow-x: hidden;
    }

    /* ===== NAVBAR (SAME AS INDEX) ===== */
    .navbar {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      padding: 20px 40px;
      background: rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
      backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
      position: sticky;
      top: 0;
      z-index: 10;
    }

    .navbar .brand a {
      font-size: 1.8rem;
      font-weight: 900;
      color: #fff;
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    .navbar ul.nav-links {
      list-style: none;
      display: flex;
      gap: 25px;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }

    .navbar ul.nav-links li a {
      text-decoration: none;
      color: #fff;
      font-weight: 600;
      transition: color 0.3s ease;
    }

    .navbar ul.nav-links li a:hover {
      color: #ffd700;
    }

    .nav-actions .btn {
      margin-left: 10px;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      border-radius: 6px;
      font-weight: bold;
      text-decoration: none;
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
      cursor: pointer;
    }

    .btn.primary {
      background: #fff;
      color: #4e73df;
      border: none;
    }

    .btn.primary:hover {
      background: #e6e6e6;
    }

    .btn.secondary {
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
      border: 2px solid #fff;
      color: #fff;
    }

    .btn.secondary:hover {
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.35);
    }

    /* ===== MAIN CONTENT ===== */
    .about-container {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      min-height: 80vh;
      padding: 60px 20px;
    }

    .about-card {
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
      backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
      padding: 40px 50px;
      border-radius: 16px;
      box-shadow: 0 12px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.25);
      text-align: center;
      max-width: 700px;
      animation: fadeIn 1s ease-in-out;
    }

    .about-card h1 {
      font-size: 2.5rem;
      font-weight: 900;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      text-shadow: 0 3px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.4);
    }

    .about-card p {
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      line-height: 1.6;
      opacity: 0.9;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .about-card .hero-buttons {
      margin-top: 30px;
    }

    .hero-buttons .btn.primary {
      background: #ffd700;
      color: #1c1c1c;
      padding: 14px 28px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      font-weight: bold;
      text-decoration: none;
      transition: all 0.3s ease-in-out;
    }

    .hero-buttons .btn.primary:hover {
      background: #e6c200;
    }

    .hero-buttons .btn.secondary {
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.25);
      color: #fff;
      border: 2px solid #fff;
      padding: 14px 28px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      font-weight: bold;
      text-decoration: none;
      transition: all 0.3s ease-in-out;
    }

    .hero-buttons .btn.secondary:hover {
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.45);
    }

    /* ===== FOOTER (SAME AS INDEX) ===== */
    footer {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 25px 20px;
      background: rgba(0,0,0,0.25);
      backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
      color: #fff;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      margin-top: 40px;
    }

    footer ul.footer-links {
      list-style: none;
      padding: 0;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 15px;
      margin: 10px 0 0 0;
    }

    footer ul.footer-links li a {
      color: #ffd700;
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    footer ul.footer-links li a:hover {
      text-decoration: underline;
    }

    @keyframes fadeIn {
      from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(-20px); }
      to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .about-card h1 { font-size: 2rem; }
      .about-card { padding: 30px 25px; }
    }

    @media (max-width: 480px) {
      .navbar { flex-direction: column; gap: 15px; }
      .about-card h1 { font-size: 1.8rem; }
      .about-card p { font-size: 1rem; }
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body class="about-body">
  <!-- ===== Navbar ===== -->
  <nav class="navbar">
    <div class="brand">
      <a href="/">HelloStore</a>
    </div>
    <ul class="nav-links">
      <li><a href="/">Home</a></li>
      <li><a href="/products">Products</a></li>
      <li><a href="/about" style="color: #ffd700;">About</a></li>
      <li><a href="/contact">Contact</a></li>
    </ul>
    <div class="nav-actions">
      <a href="/users/login" class="btn secondary">Login</a>
      <a href="/users/register" class="btn primary">Register</a>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <!-- ===== About Content ===== -->
  <main class="about-container">
    <div class="about-card">
      <h1>About HelloStore</h1>
      <p>HelloStore is your trusted one-stop shop for school and office essentials. Weâ€™re passionate about providing top-quality products with style and convenience in mind.</p>
      <p>Our goal is to make your work and study life easier by offering items that inspire productivity, creativity, and organization.</p>

      <div class="hero-buttons">
        <a href="/" class="btn primary">Back to Home</a>
        <a href="/contact" class="btn secondary">Contact Us</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>

  <!-- ===== Footer ===== -->
  <footer>
    <p>&copy; 2025 HelloStore. All rights reserved.</p>
    <ul class="footer-links">
      <li><a href="/terms">Terms & Conditions</a></li>
      <li><a href="/privacy">Privacy Policy</a></li>
    </ul>
  </footer>
</body>
</html>
